{"tid":836613,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無有iphone3g出嗰陣就買機？當時帶iphone係有咩感覺？？","createTime":"2018-09-25T19:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T12:23:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"433915eb5e2620ee2cb843f8f2c14852a2b4cf85","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:35:40.000Z","msg":"係咪好多人注視你？"},{"pid":"e5eb7649efd2fdb593e8bc9ec6c32f7b478554a2","tid":836613,"uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:44:05.000Z","msg":"2G 問我係玩具定遊戲機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091e2affb96b8fb6d0863166c3ed44f2d52020bb","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"第1部iphone係3gs<br />\n係阿爸無啦啦買左返黎送俾我，勁開心<br />\n<br />\n果陣仲讀緊中學，d Frd 全部仲用緊Nokia/sony果d機<br />\n老師都冇乜見到係用iphone，我拎左返學都唔敢拎出黎玩<br />\n<br />\n跟住andriod開始普及，平過iphone又有得玩智能電話，好多同學都轉左andriod機<br />\n但佢地又想玩iOS d game，所以又會買埋iPod touch<br />\n之後去到iphone4定唔知4s就真係個個同學都轉晒做iphone咁濟<br />\n<br />\n原先貪平用andriod果班最後都換晒iPhone<br />\n但我就仲係用緊3gs，一用就用左4年"},{"pid":"a6b268439fec85d80f61ba83765cb1854b2458d2","tid":836613,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:46:28.000Z","msg":"嗰陣冇人會覺得iphone係勁野 純粹得個貴字 多數人都用window phone/blackberry"},{"pid":"e597b411f52c19723008c6fc93b5fdab7440fcbb","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:52:18.000Z","msg":"我第一部係iPhone 3G<br />\n都陪伴左我好多讀書時既歲月<img src=\"http://goo.gl/KWgmak\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FKWgmak&h=8c01e2be&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n果時d同學仲用緊nXX Nokia 電話多"},{"pid":"d5173c73aedb18d46a9b05425740bfe13efd4b8b","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:54:14.000Z","msg":"當年係美國買左部iphone2g番嚟用 <br />\n我覺得自己係人生贏家 <br />\n去上海做嘢d同事見到我部電話個個搶嚟玩 <br />\n<br />\nBtw 當年JB真係好難"},{"pid":"3e4aa575b802be9df42484c6ee638a89610d4ea3","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:57:04.000Z","msg":"我不嬲唔追電話，<br />\n之前每一部都係0機0預繳價特平續約plan我先會換 <br />\n果時3g 一開始得3有上台出，<br />\n我屋企人間公司仲有3xxx預繳無限上3g平plan，<br />\n開頭以為所謂既電話上網好似window Mobil 咁垃圾，<br />\n點之拎黎試下上高登，<br />\n發覺只係慢電腦少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二日即刻請假衝去佢公司，用佢地個plan出機，<br />\n好記得以前每日要搭個幾兩個鐘車返工，<br />\n冇書睇果時真係悶到痴線，<br />\n有時一本漫畫一程車翻睇幾次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好記得果時收工一上車可以即刻上高登果種喜悅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時高登仲好多野睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4596f077afdc012d595704c9cfc27b499ba72350","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:00:25.000Z","msg":"當年iphone 3g一出勁型 <br />\n係街上facebook同msn d人覺得好神奇 <br />\n係facebook講野仲會有句via Facebook for iPhone 簡直係身份像徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年乜功能都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連單獨del call log都冇 <br />\n轉wallpaper唔洗諗 用黑色啦 (winterboard啦) <br />\n拍片冇 只可以影相 (仲記得cycoder) <br />\n連中文打字都冇 要手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (所以買左iacces百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\nos2年代control centre (sbsettings <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n同埋冇multitasking 每次開app都重新load (裝backgrounder) <br />\n冇icloud (用google contacts) <br />\n<a href=\"http://me.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fme.com&d=QPh9qvvmeiGxVTY%2FFfJyqp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5f9f4d9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">me.com</a>要比錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多諗到再講&hellip;想當年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7097ee60f69e355b552e8d77652c25c068c79da7","tid":836613,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:09:22.000Z","msg":"之前仲用緊Nokia<br />\n之後出左部3GS<br />\n第一次拎出黎玩，好靚，好順<br />\nMulti touch放大張相，好神奇<br />\n(以前Nokia仲係double click放大相)"},{"pid":"2c22a270ae128af8885b418c6bc0b4c8e5d70e65","tid":836613,"uid":35660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:31:01.000Z","msg":"3g 3gs 都有 <br />\n<br />\n個時用 大家都淨係話貴<br />\n無乜人用<br />\n<br />\n個時記得仲用緊 ICQ 同 MSN<br />\n坐緊車 online 啲朋友覺得好神奇囉"},{"pid":"c027d8c07c8428f8ab5eb7d0dcf8117243df8e45","tid":836613,"uid":178188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T20:38:33.000Z","msg":"認真當時攞出黎用真係好多人望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71be125b8ba0aa30747acff1f49c46e25c4a24f3","tid":836613,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5eb7649efd2fdb593e8bc9ec6c32f7b478554a2","tid":836613,"uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:44:05.000Z","msg":"2G 問我係玩具定遊戲機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T22:26:17.000Z","msg":"記得屋企人問我果部2G係咪 股霸"},{"pid":"913c023f12fac753e65ab7baecbcddad7eaed310","tid":836613,"uid":160263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T22:49:24.000Z","msg":"究竟樓主有幾多重人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fed9277801cf664fc08902178adb30e9f277772","tid":836613,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"第一個陣考